Class MyQueue<E>

java.lang.Object
implementations.MyQueue<E>
Type Parameters:
E - element type
All Implemented Interfaces:
utilities.QueueADT<E>
public class MyQueue<E> extends Object implements utilities.QueueADT<E>
This is a Queue Abstract Data Type that stores a type of element. Implements the QueueADT interface. Stores all elements within a MyDLL Doubly Linked List method. Automatically grows when capacity is reached.
Author:
Mikael Ly
